  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2644040/extras/ac2a38ada542bf97a9db0690fbe66aaf.avif?t=1703145589\" width=486 height=174 /></span><br>Sit down, roll over and dogpile onto the action 'cause its time for <strong>Ruff City</strong>! Play as Lucky the Dog- punch, kick and spin your way to victory through 4 stages of <i>PUG-ilistic</i> mayhem. Ruff City is a classic beat em' up game featuring local co-op and a pack of <i>fur-ocious</i> bosses to overcome. Grab a friend and take to the streets!<br>(Controller required for Multiplayer)",
